✅ TaskMaster - Your Ultimate Productivity Companion 🚀
Welcome to TaskMaster! 🎯 A sleek, powerful, and user-friendly task management application designed to supercharge your productivity. Built with modern web technologies, TaskMaster helps you organize tasks, track progress, and stay motivated with a delightful and intuitive interface. 🌟

🌈 What is TaskMaster?
TaskMaster is your go-to tool for managing daily tasks with ease and style. Whether you're juggling work, personal projects, or life goals, TaskMaster empowers you to stay organized, prioritize effectively, and celebrate your achievements. With a modern design and smart features, it’s the perfect companion for anyone looking to master their tasks! 💪

✨ Key Features

✅ Robust Task Management  

Assign priority levels and deadlines to keep your tasks on track 📅  
Drag-and-drop task reordering for effortless organization 🔄


🎨 Beautiful & Responsive Design  

Switch between Light, Dark, or System themes for a personalized experience 🌙☀️  
Fully responsive for seamless use on any device 📱💻


📊 Analytics & Achievements  

Track your progress with insightful analytics 📈  
Unlock achievements to stay motivated and celebrate milestones 🏆


🔔 Smart Notifications  

Stay informed with timely task reminders and updates 🔔


👤 Personalized User Profiles  

Customize your profile and preferences to make TaskMaster your own 🌟


📅 Interactive Calendar  

Advanced date selection for planning tasks with precision 🗓️




🛠️ Tech Stack



Technology
Purpose



React 18+ ⚛️
Dynamic and responsive frontend


TypeScript 📘
Type-safe development for reliability


Tailwind CSS 🎨
Utility-first CSS for stunning designs


Shadcn UI 🧩
Modern, reusable UI components


Lucide Icons 🌈
Sleek and customizable icon set


date-fns 📅
Lightweight and powerful date handling


Vite ⚡
Fast and efficient build tooling



📂 Project Structure
├── 📁 public/                   # Static assets (images, favicon, etc.)
├── 📁 src/
│   ├── 📁 components/           # Reusable UI components
│   │   ├── ✅ tasks/            # Task management components
│   │   ├── 📅 calendar/         # Interactive calendar components
│   │   ├── 📊 analytics/        # Progress and achievement tracking
│   │   └── 🧩 ui/               # Shared Shadcn UI components
│   ├── 📁 hooks/                # Custom React hooks
│   ├── 📁 utils/                # Utility functions
│   ├── ⚛️ App.tsx               # Main application component
│   └── 🚀 main.tsx              # Vite entry point
├── 📄 .gitignore                # Ignored files for Git
├── 📦 package.json              # Project dependencies
├── ⚙️ vite.config.ts           # Vite configuration
├── 🎨 tailwind.config.ts       # Tailwind CSS configuration
└── 📘 tsconfig.json            # TypeScript configuration


🚀 Get Started
Ready to take control of your tasks? Follow these steps to set up TaskMaster locally! 🌟
1. Clone the Repository 📥
git clone https://github.com/krishyadav90/TaskMaster.git
cd TaskMaster

2. Install Dependencies 📦
npm install

3. Launch the Development Server 🚀
npm run start

Visit http://localhost:5173 in your browser to start organizing! 🌐

🔐 Environment Variables
If integrating external services (e.g., APIs for notifications or analytics), create a .env file in the root directory:
VITE_API_URL=https://your-api-endpoint
VITE_API_KEY=your-api-key


